  <package>com.octo.captcha</package>
  
  <description>
  <![CDATA[
  <b>CAPTCHA</b>, for <b>C</b>ompletely <b>A</b>utomated <b>P</b>ublic <b>T</b>est to tell <b>H</b>umans and <b>C</b>omputers 
  <b>A</b>part, is a test based on several cognitives puzzles based on challenging problems
  of artificial intelligence. These tests are to prevent computer programs or
  robots to obtain information, by challenging with a problem that only human can
  resolve.
  <p/>
  Several tests has been specified:
  <p/>
  <ul>
  <li><b>Gimpy</b>: This test is based on distorted image and text. Gimpy randomly
  generate a distorted and corrupted text in an image, and asks to the user to 
  type the word displayed in the image.
  </li>
  <li><b>Sound</b>: This test is based on distorted sound. It randomly generate a distorted 
  sound and asks to user to type the word which was played.
  </li>
  <li><b>Pix</b>: This test randomly pick 6 images which have on object in common. Then it
  asks to user to type the object in common.
  </li>
  <li><b>Bongo</b>: This is a logical an memory test based on shape recognition.
  </li>
  </ul>
  ]]>
  </description>
  
